DIE algemene jaarvergadering (AJV) van die Cart Horse Protection Association vind volgende week plaas. Die gasspreker is Tozie Zokufa, â€™n bekende welsynkonsultant wat hoofsaaklik met plaasdiere werk. Van die organisasies wat betrokke is, is Compassion in World Farming, Humane Society International, Humane Education Trust, Animal Voice en Pan African Animal Welfare Alliance. Begin Zokufa is aktief in die Africa Network for Animal Welfare, Cape Animal Welfare Forum, World Animal Net, Soil for Life, Coalition for African Animal Welfare Organisations en die World Animal Day. Die AJV begin 18:00 op 17 September by die River Club, Liesbeekparkweg, Observatory, Kaapstad.